{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/975630/extras/03_build_dinosaurs.gif?t=1692946126\" /><br><br>In an alternate world, giant fossils are being unearthed across the globe. You\u2019re recruited by renegade scientist Dr Peggy Noon to help prove her outlandish theory that \u201cdinosaurs\u201d once existed.<br><br>Travel to uncharted locations, dig up fossils and piece them together to prove that dinosaurs once roamed the earth. Your search takes a dangerous turn when you uncover the mysterious Particle 58, and when Peggy goes missing it is up to you to reveal the truth behind the lie: that these magnificent creatures hold the key to understanding our past\u2014and a warning for our future.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore Environments</h2>Climb, rappel, chop vines, break-apart rocks, and solve puzzles to find fossils.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/975630/extras/01_explore_environments.gif?t=1692946126\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Uncover Fossils</h2>Use your pickaxe to break open digsites, then throw your drop bin to teleport fossils back to your tent.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/975630/extras/02_uncover_fossils.gif?t=1692946126\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Build Dinosaurs</h2>Like a three-dimensional jigsaw puzzle, piece the dinosaur together and watch it come alive before your eyes.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/975630/extras/03_build_dinosaurs.gif?t=1692946126\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Bring Dinosaurs To Life</h2>Place the final fossil and watch dinosaurs come alive in front of your eyes.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/975630/extras/04_build_dinosaurs.gif?t=1692946126\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Watch the Environment Change</h2>Watch t